Insider Activity


Individual




John Y. Televantos



Dr. John Y. Televantos is on the Board of Directors at Balchem Corp. and Velsicol Chemical Corp. Dr. Televantos was previously employed as President by Aqualon Co., Vice President by Hercules, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Foamex International, Inc., Vice President by Lyondell Chemical Co., Vice President by ARCO Chemical Co., a Board Member by Eastman Specialties Corp., a Board Member by IDQ Holdings, Inc., a Board Member by Source Refrigeration & HVAC, Inc., and a Board Member by Vertellus Specialties, Inc. He also served on the board at Interdynamics, Inc., Novolyte Technologies, Inc., Reilly Corp. and Union Carbide Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of London and a doctorate degree from the University of London.



